txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Tough sword sheaths from the Orcs north of Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'This will certainly relieve us all of some of our fears. Thank you.'
'As if the goblins were not bad enough, now we know that there are Orcs to our north. Can you bring proof that you are whittling their number down?'

Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of tough sword sheaths.
Deliver the tough sword sheaths to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
You have accepted a task to deliver tough sword sheaths to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith in the North Downs. You can find tough sword sheaths on Orcs north of Amon Raith.
Wanted: Tough sword sheaths from the Orcs north of Amon Raith.
